The need for speed The Run competes across America.
Revision
Originally a race without a problem becomes a set of stupid errors of people who have nothing to do with a routine morning shift at work.
It fills up to a certain extent the ambition of everyone but it is no use if nobody wants to do something more.
The new party subtitled The Run produced great expectations before his exit.
He promised to take a new direction with the race series Need for Speed already old and break a game from jouables parties which would not only with points.
So we were curious how the passages will be added during which the main hero fate of his car and does what he wants.
As already happens in the NFS series, the result is completely different than what we atttendait.
These are potentially running games arcades, but the whole derives downwards because of a few unnecessary mistakes that already exist for several years.
They are not really errors but rather an expression of an incomprehensible idleness of the developers.
The adventure begins very well.
You are caught up in the adventure whose main hero Jack has emotional problems and solve them to participate in illegal racing across America.
You sit behind the wheel on the west coast in San Francisco and your mission is the first in New York.
The idea has some interesting points.
The route is divided into ten steps and then more than 50 races.
The result is that each race on a different route and steps in different environments that differ quite well with each other and are interesting.
The player did not feel a moment that the game offered something similar.
Some environments are also quite nice even if the technical level chart is the same type as the previous series.
Finally, this is not the end of the world.
But driving through the desert in autumn landscapes or in highly snowy mountains is very visually pleasing.
The tests are more from time to time with an atypical element.
For example in the desert you find yourself in a sandstorm you significantly reduces visibility.
Then in the mountains, you must pay attention to what an avalanche you cannot fall.
However the different races are tidily one behind the other.
There is only a small number, but that is enough.
There are moments you strive to surpass the number requested adversaries (as in a classic race) and then you will be running against the clock (classic duel with the stopwatch) and then still awaits you another duel with an adversary.
From time to time you also police entering the game and trying to make the situation reportedly rarely.
The novelty is the passages out vehicle.
Rather, it is interactive animation una when most of the time Jack flees to someone and you must help by banging on the right button at the right time.
Nothing complicated.
What is surprising is that there are fewer moments of this type that what you want (to be concrete, there were only three).
The result is this because this element will not hamper and place within the context described above, the elements that make up the game.
The model of conduct is in the tradition of previous games.
This means that currently there is nothing extraordinary, but we cannot say that this is negative.
With regard to the realistic simulation you will have to go elsewhere.
But while one can find better in the conccurrence model of conduct goes very well with the type of design races.
So everything is ok.
The problems begin to appear after a certain time.
The diffférence model of conduct, the collision is not yet ready.
We do not expect this game a complicated and deformation of collisions, but when you are not in a collision with any object, the slightest idea how behaves your car, so this is not completely fit.
During the tight overruns you sometimes touch each other slightly but otherwise your car share in voltiges mad.
Or is in tatters.
Thanks to restart system that is not really a problem, but it really upsets.
The recovery is so that when you have broken the figure or you are out in the decor, the game takes you back to the time of the last item on the route.
But you have not only 5 reboots.
When you have used the 5 reboots you need to start the game from the start.
It is more a tool, if something is not happening, here on which you can really count.
Sometimes the reboots do not help, and we must find a solution in remémorrant memory the piece of itinerary.
The major fault of this game is that the same actions are in the same places.
For example, there are some turns that we need to move a certain way otherwise does not pass.
Otherwise you meet on a given location "civilian" vehicles still in the same configuration you conclude first, fifth, advanced 5 seconds or a minute late.
What angry are the situations when you see easily pass the adversary between two cars oncoming and when you arrive, you, you must either be put aside and conturner or curb.
It is equal if you go to him because it is "calculated" in such a way that the situation it is always very close to your nose.
Opponents have other advantages.
During the time of the game, you arrive in some places, again regardless of the time, and you always have the same adversary above you in the same place.
This irritates the most end when you go on a long bridge in the opposite direction.
The enemy must pass in front of you.
When he goes before you hide the sight of the other vehicles in the opposite direction and you enter collided many times.
It is understandable that the purpose of this game is to do something exciting and full of adrédaline, but it is clear that you are bored quickly.
And it is a shame, because through a simple conduct model of the game is interesting and places with action that you do not have the time to monitor everything that happens.
And it is equal if it is because of the concept of 50 unique itineraries, that the racing is such that there is no chance to be bored or something else.
The original idea is the change of car during races.
You must pay attention to gasoline pumps on routes because you can change cars, however, most of the time that you enough.
The cars are divided into three categories.
Sports cars are ideal for cities, big-engined American for straight highways and super sports cars to exotic garb on highly technical led by example on the switchback roads in the mountains.
And the mode of challenges, which are racing in particular places you know adventure goes very well with the main scheme in history.
You get not only medals but also experience points are added to your profile that is common to the challenges and adventure.
When you have reached the highest level of driver, various objects begin to unlock:
It connects on-line with the Autolog function among others compare your results with those of other players and provide other functions in the community.
One of the hardest blows to understand the situation of the last race of the adventure.
You arrive with your car in the underground tunnel (sounds like where you are driving in the dark on the tracks (it looks).
Your speedometer indicates you between 150 and 200 km/hour (beforehand) and behind you is a subway train that sends you the car directly to scrap.
The editorial we had a discussion for a few days to determine whether someone has really thought in the creation of this game or whether the authors we really like idiots.
The technical part of the game is not extra, but the visual part is generally pleasant and in some cases really super.
The discomfort is that in more extreme situations, imagery is not the level and in some cases dramatically.
This is primarily in accidents with a large number of participants when a fluid imagery you no longer serves any purpose.
The audio portion is good and the runway is the choice.
In order to appeal to the greatest number, particularly the most young audiences a new soundtrack was created in the style "I mix everything," but we can expect that nobody will buy the stake for music.
Overall impression of Need for Speed: the Run is really confused.
If the game did not have these stupid mistakes we could say without fear that it is the best NTS production in recent years.
But this game gives the impression of not being finished.
Amusement is really good, but you are preparing to ensure that the mistakes you pat in the eye with the force of a reflector airfield.
The velvet Students in conjunction with the choirs of Charles University
The festival Festa Academica proposes for the third time the festivities that connect International Day student with the anniversary of the Velvet Revolution with a party music.
During the festival occur 20 choirs of upper secondary schools and classes.
The highlight of the festival consists of two concerts orgnisés on 17 November.
"Charles University has an important part in this festival."
"Among the choruses, there is the Choir of the Faculty of Pédagogie and Humanities, the festival's committee seat Rector Vaclav Hampl," says the head of the organizing team Jakub Calou.
The highlight of the festival is the concert choir of secondary schools and classes unfolding with free entry on November 17 from 14 hours in the area before the National Library technical Dejvice.
The programme is the composition of the well-known Czech musician Karel Ruzicka, Celebration Jazz mass.
In the evening unfolds the concert "students Velvet" in the national Vinohrady during which occur choirs graduate schools as well as that of Charles University.
The Festa Academica aims not only to celebrate with dignity the International Day of students and recall the 22 anniversary of the Velvet Revolution, but also to present to the public music chorus of the highest level and develop creative cooperation of young people.
The main organizer is the Union of Czech prospect in cooperation with the school Jan Kepler.
Any action is placed under the aegis of Bohuslav Svoboda, Mayor of Prague and Vaclav Hampl, Rector of the Charles University.
The festival takes place from November 16 to 20 in Prague and Pardubice.
The program also proposes concerts of high-level meetings msicales, a student happening and other activities.
Interested parties will find all the information on the Internet pages www.festaacademica.cz. festival
Vicenova, Ambassador near the European Union:
The Czechs are behaving like négativistes and Eurosceptics
" The Lisbon Treaty has radically removed the balance between the institutions '
"I did not expect such a harsh war."
"It will take 5.6 years before the situation is calm and that all players are accustomed to their new role," as well as Miléna Vicenova began his presentation at the Law Faculty of the Czech ambassador near the European Union.
When she was able to describe the various organs of the EU and their relations so understandable and visible, to the point that a large number of speakers from the Faculty of Law of Charles University might envy, it has shown how it takes its motto "understandable and openly about Europe" very seriously.
Mrs Vicenova paid tribute to the work of Herman Van Rompuye, the new permanent President of the European Council.
"From the outset resounded criticism that it is bland, that it is a round-of-leather, that it cannot rempplir any mission and I must say that it has cut the breath to everybody because it takes its role to perfection."
"This is a man who listens to 27 member states, communicate with them and has a clear vision of the direction of Europe."
She said the new post of High Representative for Foreign Affairs and Defence Policy within the framework of an answer to the question: "who is that the European Union?" "what phone number do I call?" As an important step towards the uniqueness and greater readability of EU policy states, such as China or India.
Nobody wants to ban our syrecky (cheese cooked that feels very strong) 
Mrs Vicenova also referred to the agenda that has lived lives and live in a time near the European Council.
She called the Czech presidency two years of success.
The Czech have solved the growing financial crisis, the gas crisis or hosted a summit for Oriental Partnership.
She called the fall of the Government very negative and has damaged the image of the Czech Republic.
The Czech representation to the EU is currently very busy.
In the words of Madam Ambassador, "activity has beaten its full" not only for the presidency, but also for the financial crisis that continues to be resolved again now.
It must approve the new septimal EU budget which becomes very complicated due to the current economic situation.
As it would appear that the budget will be thin and savings, what branch will have priority, which countries will be helped the most, the least, is to be resolved in the context of future negotiations.
Madam Ambassador recalled its slogans with which she arrived in Brussels for a Europe that is understandable. "
" I definitely don't like the abbreviations, foreign words, jargon that nobody understands.
As must understand the citizens that it is true that in Brussels no rings or twisted gherkins, bananas differemment large or that nobody has forbidden to syrecky. "
She wants to make better use of the EU's environment and see more Czechs in European institutions.
A multi-speed Europe awaits us
According to Ambassador the Czechs have a reputation for being Eurosceptics and people who do not see things in their more negative than positive.
It is sorry to see if a small Czech representation in European institutions.
The fault is the result, according to several factors, such as the timidity of our candidates, their inability to write a letter of motivation and a low support for the Czech Republic.
A Czech presidency success then stressed the strength and the cooperation of the Visegrad Group.
" Believe me, when come to me the Poles, the Magyar, Slovak, French said to me: ' Wow, what is that you are there, that is still the Visegrad group? " And it is not at all happy. "
According to Mrs Vicenova, in the near future are new tough rules on budgetary policy that await the member countries.
It is the concept of a two-speed Europe, if not at different speeds, which prevails rather than a "new European Federation."
"We have countries in the euro zone and other outside of the area."
"We have the Schengen area, we also have the institute of enhanced cooperation."
First it was said that cooperation among the countries that want it and those who do not wish to remain in their corner. "
"There will be a lot of institutes of this type, and there will be a Europe really two-speed," expects Mrs Vicenova.
From this point of view, she also appreciated the mission of the Czech Republic and Herman Van Rompuye to determine the basis under which all the themes that have an impact on the EU must be discussed between all members of the EU and not just the memebres in the eurozone.
History of a mark:
The innovative IBM begins the second century of its existence
If someone should seek the word expresses closer to the IBM strategy, the closest would be "the long term."
For a wide audience IBM is the symbol of the technological revolution, is a firm perceived as very current and yet since its creation it has passed 100 years.
The basis of this long-term strategy has been thrown by the first head of the firm, the visionary Thomas J. Watson Sr.
He has left this slogan that many global problems can be solved if people are willing to consider.
Its slogan "PENSE!" Became the imprint that life is going to develop a future giant (and also the title of the internal magazine that IBM began to publish in 1935).
It was the basis of the culture of the company soignement developed by Watson.
For us, IBM means thinking long-term continuous movements directed towards the future.
IBM has survived 100 years thanks to the fact that she always remained true to its core values, however, has not been afraid to change all the others around it.
This has helped us during our first century transforming technology, business and society.
We hope that in the second century we will achieve even more " délaré for the anniversary, the current director of the firm, Samuel J. Palmisano.
A well-prepared system
Watson, in the 1930s, began to take care of its employees as Bata in the Czech Republic - people from IBM were the only one of the first American employees have paid vacation, an employer-paid insurance plus a uniform elegant employee and a well-developed system of rewards for inventors and commmerciaux.
Similarly, IBM has a system of relationships with the client well developed.
The company was brilliant early in the discovery of talent, as one of the first firms to have abolished all forms of discrimination and thus could have a choice.
The current plan is completely in the spirit of the anti-discriminatory strategy since it will be a woman, Virginia Rometty - who should replace Palmisano at the head of IBM.
The latter worked at IBM for 30 years and currently holds the position of Head of Sales, Marketing and Strategy.
IBM in recent years is what is called the jamy, brain-storming online from what are far from future strategies and innovations.
It is not surprising that he has a lot of ideas - the firm nearly 500000 people who work.
An institution with a good name
It is the internal and external image of the company to ensure a secure position in the areas of business.
"Since the beginning, IBM had a concept rather institution as a technology firm," said drawing, Professor of Economics at the School of Economics at Harvard and author of the book on IBM.
"IBM is not a technlogique firm but a firm that helps solve problems in the world of business, using its technology," added Geogre Colony of consulting firm Forrester Research.
As the firm itself, there is a difference between entering the market and create this market.
IBM - or the "big Blue," as it is called familiarly in the United States with regard to its slogan, in 100 years it has grown to become one of the largest global companies.
It is obviously the most versatile technology firm - it develops software, hardwares, infrastructure, housing, services Council at the level of the server products up to nanotechnology.
It has many patents of all American technology firms and five of its employees received a Nobel Prize.
Among his discoveries stands, for example, the distributor of tickets, the payment card, the swap, the bar code or the disk.
IBM has been this year with $220 billion, the second-largest technology company by market capitalization (the first is Apple), when for the first time it passed in 1996, Microsoft.
Overview in advance
It is not all innovations and workmanship that took customer preference and IBM - for example, has failed the bet on its own operating system OS/2, Prodige online service or the IBM computer PCjr:
"When your business is built on the movement in advance you cannot émotionellement remain ensconced on the past," said Samuel J. Palmisano.
For this, IBM has no problem to build bases on many platforms and when they do not operate it.
Unlike example conccurent Microsoft at the base stands and remains under the Windows operating system.
A technology perspective
In the IBM revenue services, which are trained to a fifth by software and hardwares, have a prominent place.
Yet in 1990 it was more of the highest motié participation representative of hardware.
From the year 2000, IBM has sold low-yielding assets for $15 billion over cettre period it has invested $58 billion in the purchase of technology prospects.
She continues in investments and even from 2008, when for the first time it has surpassed the new financial crisis.
IBM negotiates according to the precepts of its first chief Thomas J. Watson, who during the great economic crisis has also increased its volume of investment.
It now appears that IBM passes the current crisis without being worried?
The share price IBM has progessé from 2008 rocket 120 percent, net income for the firm continues to grow.
The company's logo IBM is to change everything, but not its values.
We can expect to this flexible giant tightening other crises.
IBM history: from the cheese slices to flights in the cosmos.
IBM (IBM) was born in New York City 100 years ago; it was originally the complicated Computing Tabulating Recording Corporation.
She took the name IBM in 1924 - initially it was a brand used by a branch of a company in Canada and South America.
The basis of the future IBM was the merger of four firms whose history is linked to the year 80 of the 19th century.
They had technologies such as the "old pointeuses" clocks that recorded the arrival and departure of employees.
The architect of the new company was Charles Ranlett Flint who until 1930 chaired the Council of surveillance society.
Flint hired the head of a rival firm Thomas J. Watson to help lead the company.
The leader was then shade to the founder of the firm - it is on the ideas of Watson that are up to now the identity and culture of the company.
Watson led the firm kusqu' in 1952.
IBM, as its name, began with the production of all possible machines for business and commerce - cheese slicers and meat until the cash registers.
During the first four years in which Watson led the turnover of redoubled to reach 9 million and began the expansion of the firm in all parts of the world.
Watson was the firm if irreplaceable after 40 years of leadership is his son who occupied the director, Thomas Watson Jr.
Under his leadership, IBM began the development of artificial intelligence and developed the first programming language.
People in the 1960s and the IBM computers helped NASA has guided flights in the cosmos - Mercury, Saturn and theft in 1969 on the Moon.
Meanwhile in 1964 IBM developed the first family of computers - the IBM System/360.
The PC classic hastened the standard computer era with the IBM 5150 came on the market in 1981.
Twenty years later IBM sells its manufactures computers to the Chinese company Lenovo, but bought the company Consulting Pricewaterhouse Coopers and began to deal with advice and services with high added value.
The strategy succeeds in IBM over the past three years - is the concept Smarter Planet "a smarter planet."
Its goal is uilisation smart technology in areas not yet exploited such as transport and management of cities.
In terms of trade area IBM has developed shortly a platform "Smarter Commerce" that helps the commercial manager throughout the business cycle.
IBM has a strong history also on our territory.
She set up its branch in Czechoslovakia in 1932 when first country of Central and Eastern Europe.
Today, in addition to IBM RT, there is also the strategic outsourcing centre in Brno.
The Centre for Central and Eastern Europe headquarters in Prague, and there is also the team's research and development of the global level, which is responsible for the recognition of the floor.
