Property overrun by squatters for micro-holidays, evacuated
The invaders had 11 of the 13 apartments in the building, Balmes, 51
The 12 occupants have abandoned the property at noon yesterday without any resistance
Everything seems to indicate that the nightmare that residents number 51 Rue Balmes lived ended.
Twelve people have abandoned at noon yesterday voluntarily the building they occupied illegally and where they held micro-holidays that désespéraient neighbours by judicial order and without the need for an intervention by the police.
At the end of the operation has changed the lock of the door to prevent the situation repeats itself.
"From this day there will be an access control," claim the administrator.
The squatters who had invaded 11 of 13 apartments in the building - the rest were inhabited, has won the electrical installation and part of water, painting the walls and leave residues of any kind, especially boxes of alcoholic beverages.
The first three apartments were the scene of mass celebrations, which lasted until two days and désespéraient tenants.
Beside the building there is a disco Balmes, 51, who was also affected.
Its owner, Maria Pantinat explained to Europa Press that from the occupation of the building his case dropped an 80%.
The owner of the discotheque referred to the invaders of the property were unfair competence, because they were selling glasses to three euros, while in the club they were worth 10.
In addition, the owner of the local leisure had to respond to complaints from neighbours for noise, while, according to the problems were not caused by customers of the discotheque, but by the inhabitants of the house occupied and especially participants celebrations there, which were more frequent and intense over the past few weeks, according to the angry neighbours of the area.
The head of the discotheque explained that the problems were so great that it has reached an agreement with the owner of the building and nine-month "forgive" the rent.
The Guardia Urbana (municipal police) also confirmed that the last few weeks they had received more complaints from neighbours for this situation.
The chairman of the Municipal Group of the PP's mayor, Alberto Fernández Díaz, had asked for the past week "the immediate evacuation of the building to finish with the problems of living together and citizenship that he caused to residents and the degradation of the zone."
The popular leader explained that before the summer only one floor of the building was occupied, but the last few months the squatters had occupied all the floors of the building and almost all apartments and in some apartments there have also been flights.
It is in this sense that he added that "we must put an end to impunity and relentless against antisocial behaviour generated in the property."
Also yesterday, the Mossos (the Catalan local police evacuated a building at Nou Barris.
The police at 3.30 p.m. shifted to number 35 Rue-Mont, after receiving a call from a neighbour who had found that four people gained access to the building.
The four were arrested immediately.
Park or mountain?
The architects coincide on the appropriateness of convening beyond polemics on fees
The municipal contests on 16 doors again opens the debate on the role of Collserola in Barcelona
In the mid-1980s, in the height of the already-extinguished Corporation Métropolitaine de Barcelona (CMB), this Administration has printed posters promoting Collserola.
The brochure defined the mountain as the large park in the metropolitan Barcelona.
It also contained a comparison, in figures, with the Central Park in New York.
With the death of the CMB, in 1987, the park has become in the imagination of many people, the upper limit of Barcelona, the Catalan capital is the only one that does not move on the north-south axis, otherwise high mountain (bottom) - (sea).
The Collserola qualification as natural park is to the advantage of this idea.
The reference was no longer Central Park otherwise Yellowstone, with wild boar in the role of Yogi Bear.
This was the situation until, in September, the mayor convened a mega-competition composed by 16 competition for all access doors Collserola.
A door calls the idea of park, no doubt.
It is this, or someone wants to put doors.
The question appears alone: Collserola: Park or mountain?
The competition, both in terms of its organization as regards the reflection on the city is a topic of conversation all architects of Barcelona.
It is almost a recurring theme, including two members of this ancient caste elected speak when they recognize in an elevator.
And this is just one of the few opinions on which coincide three architects of Barcelona, university professors, who are presented.
Miguel Roldán, Daniel Modol and Marta Bayona: the competition is timely.
For Roldán, after addressing the littoral front "it is necessary to" discuss "the mountain front" because the speech Ildefons Cerda, blocks green has not been brought to an end.
" We have to start from the premise that the largest fleet of Barcelona is the beach.
Among other things for his great accessibility.
Collserola is more complex, " gave the verdict the architect for the title of " Collserola doors " contains a " lexicon trap ": it must consider " such as access to a park, but the delimitation of some areas in which we must act. "
Modol, as Roldán and Bayona with experience in the urban world, describes the proposal as "intellectual challenge" with "some perils."
The perils that are derived from "the uncertainty of the projection of public space" after the experience in the 1980s and has been in the area of the Forum, "his swan song."
The first fear is own demarcation of borders on which we can build.
"Limiting something means already set the next step," that is to say, its excess.
"We need to think about new instruments urban planning, because the current [in reference to General Plan Métropolitain (PGM) ] can cause authentic disasters."
In addition to the question, Modol opinion that, by simplifying the slope of the El Valle region Collserola "can be understood as a park, Barcelona, no."
Modol recalls that there is already a work done by the conflicting interests of Collserola " must not be lost, " thanks for the opportunity that the mayor offers his corporation to intervene in this project from the very first time. "
It means that the proximity of the mountain with the city is the safe conduct that enables architects to enter the debate, but "doubt" whether this looming technique must lead the multidisciplinary teams ("a success," he says) that it is creating: "we, the architects, should be just an instrument."
Bayona hints that the answer to the question that gives the title of this piece is complex, because of the foundations of the competition it lacks a comprehensive vision of Collserola: "we called 16-cutting competition - he says - in mountains, but there is not a longitudinal reading track and understand the area as a whole."
This is, at least in this case, he has opted to participate in the 16 contests.
In another way, a project for doors to shock in the programme and definition with the architect of the door.
In his opinion, yes, the mayor should ensure that the band immediately superior to that of Ronda Dalt should provide throughout its extension, an area of equipment that makes a gentle transition between the city and green.
Casino forgive Jonás Larrazábal and it will be released
After 72 days of provisional arrest, the legal power of Red Casino has granted forgiveness to brother of the mayor of Monterrey for the insider trial against him for alleged blackmail
After 72 years arrested, Manuel Jonás Larrazábal will be released after the statutory power of Red Casino grant forgiveness before the Second Criminal Court of the District, which follows a trial for blackmail against the brother of the mayor of Monterrey.
After the attack on the Casino Royale, the owner of the Red Casino, Sergio García Gil, has published a series of photos and videos in which Manuel Jonás allegedly demanded the payment of a quotte economic for the mayor of Monterrey allows the clandestine operation of the house.
After the public denunciation, the prosecutor has opened a criminal case against the brother of the mayor PANiste and September 2, he was arrested and kept in detention for 30 days.
After four hours in front of the Public Prosecution Service Agent 3 Offences Patrimoniaux, he was transferred to the Detention Centre 1, located in the Old Quarter of the capital of the state.
He stayed there for 49 days when he delivered a second detention order after the officer of the Public Ministry has dismissed the offences of corruption and organized crime.
19 October he was transferred to the criminal centre Cadereyta alleged to have been blackmailed with one and a half million pesos owners Red Casino; but he spent only a few hours in the detention centre average security because there were death threats against him.
The authorities have allowed him to continue the trial encased in the municipal cells of San Nicolas de los Garza.
On 25 October a catch was issued by the Clerk of the Second Criminal Court of the District, Jorge Yanez, who said that after almost two months of investigation there were sufficient evidence confirmed to determine the guilt of Jonás, such as those relating to the collection of 1.5 million pesos from representatives of the house in exchange for allowing its operation.
On Monday the legal power of Red Casino, Víctor Aldo García Gómez, appeared before Judge José Luis Pecina to seek forgiveness for the brother of the mayor of the region; therefore it could recover his freedom over the following hours.
During the legal formalities, the officer of the Public Prosecution Service attached to the Tribunal, Ramiro Arias, García Gómez questioned if the damage had been recovered and associates of the house had been the one who had granted forgiveness, but the lawyer has tried not to disclose the name.
Under the 197/2011 dossier has been granted forgiveness legal Jonás Larrazábal and later can be no claim on the lawsuit against him; it will not repair the damage and no punishment.
After the hearing of the legal power to the house at 3: 50.00 p.m. ordered the immediate release of Larrazabal Bretón.
The Clerk of the Court, Jorge Yáňez, moved up to the prison municipium San Nicolas de los Garza to communicate to Jonás that he had been legally pardoned and his case would be classified.
He will also order immediate freedom that the judge has issued.
Secretary Dionisio Pérez Jácome gives communicates the details of the air accident in which has lost his life, the Government's secretary, Francisco Blake and another seven people
The Secretariat of Communications and Transport (SCT) informed that the results highlighted on the accident in which has lost his life the Government secretary, Francisco Blake Mora and seven other people, indicate that the helicopter has shocked directly against the soil full structural integrity, but the pilot can try a forced landing.
During a press conference, Dionisio Pérez Jácome, secretary of Communications and Transport, said that before the takeoff of the aircraft, the pilot found that the climate conditions were adequate to fly.
"The elements that seem to indicate that the unit had various contacts with the soil, the blades have had contact with trees to 25 metres where the unit has lost the fuselage."
He also informed that the unit was designed to 19 people, therefore met the requirements necessary to transport personnel.
In addition, he said that the investigations in the area of impact does not relate the emergence of pieces on the ground.
" In a search has been reported that there was no parts or components of the aircraft in another location, the impact has presented structural way.
" The helicopter was designed for 19 passengers and met the requirements for transport.
The soil was a pante from seven to 30 degrees.
For the moment, the secretary has assured that a priority is to have the results as soon as possible, but the investigation could last a few months, it may last for a year.
In turn, Gilberto Lopez Meyer, director general of Airports and Services branch has ensured that the moment of impact, the helicopter state Presidential Maggiore was speed cruiser stern and happened on an ascendant soft ground.
"This information supports the hypothesis of a cruiser stern normal functioning at the time of the impact," he says.
During the press conference, the holder of the SCT, Pérez Jácome, has listed six important elements in the investigation:
Visual flight:
According to the normative aeronautics, the flight was conducted under the rules of visual flight, implying that the crew must have visibility during the flight and ground.
Weather conditions:
The reports in IMMA mentioned adequate conditions during takeoff, and as the aircraft was moving towards the border area between DF and the State of Mexico there were layers of clouds at low height.
Selected roads:
It is likely to cause cloud conditions crew has sought a zone of lower height and greater visibility into the valley of Cuernavaca.
Location of the impact.
Details of the impact and the last recording of the aircraft on radar coincide, probably before the impact, there has been no loss of control or alteration of the flight path.
Dispersion of the remains of the aircraft in a small area:
The information available so far suggests that the impact took place on a trajectory and right side.
The model of dispersion of the remains of the aircraft suggests that the helicopter was hit against the soil in structural integrity.
It has not detected traces of fire or explosion:
In the disaster there is still no trace in the remains of the aircraft from one type of explosion or fire.
The latest results of the investigation indicate that the aircraft had had multiple contacts with the soil.
During the field work was found parts of the aircraft at a height of 9 thousand 200 feet above mean sea level, the soil had a slope that runs for seven dégrées 30 degrees.
The photographs show the sequence in which he was possibly désarticulé throughout his journey.
The information provides elements that seem to indicate that the helicopter may have had multiple impacts with the soil.
After a thorough search in an area more than the place surrounded around the accident has not been found scattered pieces of the aircraft, which supports the presumption that the impact took place in conditions of structural integrity.
MSS announcement protocol to find the gene for obesity
Social insurance leads an investigation to discover the gene for obesity in children and young people; this is borne by the IPN specialists
The Mexican Institute of Social Insurance (IMSS) announced that he is leading an investigation to discover the gene for obesity in children and young people, called protocol ' genetics of obesity in children and adolescents who will have the markers associated with being overweight.
In a statement, the head of the Investigation Unit Médicale in Biochemistry Hospital of specialities of the National Medical Center of the 20th century, Miguel Cruz López, explained that it had formed a multidisciplinary team of doctors, nurses, nutritionists and attend social.
This team is supported by specialists and postgraduate students of the National Institute of Public Health (INSP) and the Center for Investigation and Advanced Studies (Cinvestav) Polytechnic National Institute (IPN).
The investigation are invited to participate population with or without the right to stand for sports units of the IMSS participating in Valle de México, where is the evidence to minors every Saturday from 8: 00.00 p.m.
He stressed that the protocol began in the Sports Cuauhtémoc Unit (Estado de México Poniente) and from October 8, the activity is taking place in the Sports unit Nezahualcóyolt (Estado de México Oriente).
After reaching the goal of raising $500 or 600 minors, the study will continue in the Sports Unit Independencia (south of Distrito Federal) and finally in the Sports Unit Morelos (north of Distrito Federal.
He explained that the purpose of this investigation and e know the components and the importance of genetics in regard to the development of obesity and identify among children and young Mexican risk factors to prevent the onset of chronic degenerative diseases.
As we celebrate on November 14, the World Diabetes Day, he mentioned that the goal is to bring together three thousand children and young people between six and 14 years, with the consent and under the supervision of their parents, for the implementation of specific questionnaires related to food.
They will also be requested on their physical activity and their history of family inheritance of their illnesses, to avoid the risk factors that trigger ailments such as diabetes or kidney failure.
He detailed that Saturday will apply to all participants anthropometric measurements (weight, height, girth size), blood pressure, determining levels of glucose, triglycerides, cholesterol and insulin and genetic (trying to identify people associated with childhood obesity.
Cruz López pointed out that this investigation is the result of the concern of health professionals for the alarming weight gain in the case of minors.
' The health surveys in 1999 and 2006 reported that in just six years there has been an increase in the case of boys, 77 percent in obesity and in the case of girls of 47 percent; as regards the overweight has also seen a dramatic increase, " stressed the IMSS.
He said that the justification for research markers is based on the fact that the country's population is different from the other by his genetic history.
He informed that, on average, the Mexicans have a 65 percent of heredity Indo-American, 30 percent and a five percent African and this condition is reflected in the people associated with diabetes and overweight.
He explained that, in general, the genetics of obesity is reflected in the inability to combust the excess energy that burns (calories), which is deposited in the form of fat.
The researcher explained that the direct benefit for participants is the full assessment of children, which can detect if they are overweight or obese.
Ila even said that the presence of dark colour folds (acanthosis) on the neck and forearm indicate the likelihood of having metabolic alterations and even pre-diabetes.
The information is managed in a confidential manner, doctors call the written to parents, which are explained each of the measures and changes in lifestyle that they must make to prevent disease.
Cruz López explained that there are three main components that cause overweight, obesity and other chronic conditions: the sedentarism, which is the lack of physical activity daily, remain most of the day sitting in front of the TV and use transport instead to walk short distances.
Another reason is the high caloric intake, it is the largest consumption of sugary drinks, carbohydrates (tamales pâté - meat to maize flour wrapped in leaves of corn, bread, pizza, hamburgers, etc.) with a high content of fat and protein and genetics analysed in this protocol.
Asphalt UNAM would avoid the blackcurrants
Rafael Herrera, researcher at the School of Chemistry of UNAM, develops asphalt polymer modified to produce a mixture with a better performance, regardless of environmental conditions and temperature
If the reported that the streets were resolved, it would no longer be necessary to repair about 200 thousand blackcurrants each season of rain in the metropolitan area of Valle de México, warns Rafael Herrera Nájera, a researcher at the School of Chemistry (FQ) UNAM, which ensured that if the process of construction and maintenance of oil is adequate, blackcurrants could be reduced or even eliminated.
During its conference A technological opinion on the blackcurrants, organized within the framework of the International Year of Chemistry, he announced that the laboratory, which is responsible for developing asphalt polymer modified to produce a mixture with characteristics similar to those of asphalt, but with greater mechanical resistance, both high as low temperatures.
Herrera Nájera has estimated that this type of modified asphalt could be used in places where the climate is extremely hot, as some cities in the north of the country, to improve the performance and, therefore, the training of cassis.
He explained that the asphalt, the heaviest share of oil, is a set of molecules of hydrocarbons, molecules with a heavier molecular weight, called asphaltenes and molecules with a low molecular weight, called malthènes, which together give the paved his characteristic viscoelastic behaviour.
The viscoelastic behaviour of asphalt is the fact that, at high temperatures, nearly 180 degrees, behaves like a liquid, 120 degrees C viscosity is very large and 50 degrees C, it presents an almost solid state, while at very low temperatures, asphalt becomes brittle, he added.
This means that the resistance in the streets of asphalt is not uniform and changes during the day, according to the environmental conditions and temperature, warns the specialist in chemical engineering.
The researcher of the FQ observed that the streets of Ciudad de México in their majority were covered by a flexible, composed of six layers of materials, including the last three imply asphalt.
Among the most superficial layers is the layer of asphalt, formed by small stones drenched asphalt and compacted later.
Each small stones that form the layer, signalât is drenched year asphalt.
When vehicles are generating efforts, it allows the forces spread very well in the streets.
If we had the modified asphalt, they propagate better, opinât ingénier the chemical.
The layer of asphalt, he says, there is a final layer called layer of rotation, fieldstone fine, that is to say, the sand is also steeped in asphalt.
As it is the layer in contact with the wheels of vehicles, it must be more mechanical force that the layer of asphalt and provide grip in the street.
As part of that receives and distributes the efforts of the rotation also requires that a proper thickness and the material it is made must be treated.
The climate, especially the humidity and temperature variations, are also a very important factor to consider, especially water, he said, because they greatly affect the performance of the layer of asphalt.
When the soil is wet, water spreads inside the layer is difficult it is that way, which softened all layers of the pavement and therefore blackcurrants.
In the trial of formation, he said, the first striker is the film rolling and only later is affected the layer of asphalt, but the damage was not immediately, but it is a process that must be treated to the first signals with proper maintenance programs.
The member of the National System of Chercheurs explained that the burden of vehicles is another important factor in the formation of blackcurrants and therefore the thickness of each layer of pavement must always be linked to the burden of vehicles and ensure its satisfaction, to avoid the frequent training blackcurrants.
Rafael Herrera warned that there is still a lot to investigate and work on the asphalt, for example, bituminous emulsions, which in other countries are already on the market and help repair the blackcurrants easily and without having to use high temperatures.
